                <TextBlock FontSize="18"
                           FontStyle="Italic"
                           HorizontalAlignment="Left"  VerticalAlignment="Top"
                           Margin="10,10,0,0"
                           >
                    This program demonstrates a variety of WPF display features and techniques.
